88
00:06:15,600 --> 00:06:17,800
I will heed your teachings.

89
00:06:20,480 --> 00:06:21,560
- I'm telling you.
- I'll...

90
00:06:21,600 --> 00:06:22,680
I have to leave now.

91
00:06:22,680 --> 00:06:23,520
Where are you going?

92
00:06:23,920 --> 00:06:25,160
The old man already woke up

93
00:06:25,720 --> 00:06:27,480
