94
00:06:27,480 --> 00:06:29,320
We must be cautious
when we meet in the future.

95
00:06:29,320 --> 00:06:30,000
I don't care.

96
00:06:30,000 --> 00:06:30,720
Get away.

97
00:06:33,080 --> 00:06:34,320
You're really leaving?

98
00:06:39,760 --> 00:06:41,280
This darn old man.

99
00:06:58,520 --> 00:07:02,000
What's wrong?
What is everyone running for?

100
00:07:11,360 --> 00:07:14,000
A Yin, what happened to your butt?

101
00:07:14,560 --> 00:07:15,600
Lin A Cha,

102
00:07:15,840 --> 00:07:21,840
- Fifteen, sixteen, seventeen.
- I dare not.

103
00:07:21,880 --> 00:07:22,680
I dare not.

104
00:07:26,720 --> 00:07:29,680
Young Master, your tea must be cold now.

105
00:07:35,120 --> 00:07:40,880
- Fifteen, sixteen, seventeen.
- I was wrong. I don't dare anymore.

106
00:07:40,880 --> 00:07:41,760
I dare not.

107
00:07:44,240 --> 00:07:46,800
Dayuan, the tea is indeed a bit cold.

108
00:07:47,320 --> 00:07:48,360
