121
00:08:31,600 --> 00:08:32,960
Come to my place tonight.

122
00:08:33,680 --> 00:08:35,800
(What's happening tonight?)

123
00:08:35,920 --> 00:08:39,560
(He really wants to...
What am I thinking?)

124
